-- Makefile not yet available, it is recommended that you build with Visual Studio until one is written --


Prerequesites for compiling on Win32:

+ EXTERNAL

Boost Libraries (add to include path for the CytrusAlgLib project) - used mainly for GIL Library
Windows Platform SDK (add to include path for the WebCamLib project) - used for DirectShow camera capture

+ BUNDLED

libjpeg - you can use the bundled library (includes & linking already set-up for the project), or you can link your own (latest version)
